												"val": {
													"type": "LSString",
													"value": "Player mind flayer does a hand wave gesture and removes the globe of domination around Orpheus. \r\nThe Player (as a mind flayer) wraps their tentacles around Orpheus' face and brings their mouth over Orpheus' head. \r\nPlayer feeds CLUMSILY. Suckling noises.\r\nOrpheus' eyes dart around in pain as his brain is consumed.\r\nOnce it's done, Orpheus' head flops to the side, his head empty. "
