				"synopsis": {
					"type": "LSString",
					"value": "Orpheus is now freed from the player's assistance. They now have the option to take the Mind Flayer form, or to give Orpheus that responsibility. He is not really impressed with the tadpole in the player's head. \r\n\r\nIt's possible the player would have fought Orpheus in Intermezzo before this point, so there should be some reactivity to it."
				},
